Package: sherwood-toolbox
Version: 0.3.3
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3, python3-venv, python3-pip, python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-webkit2-4.1, xdg-utils
Maintainer: Sherwood Toolbox <support@example.com>
Description: Local estimating tools hub
 A modular Flask application that provides a hub and several
 offline-capable estimating tools (Ice & Water Shield calculator,
 Estimate Enhancer, Photo Report, and Documents generator).
